ðŸ”¹ PART 2: Azure Cloud Commands (Azure CLI)
Login
Bash
Copy code
az login
Virtual Machines
Bash
Copy code
az vm list
az vm start --name VM_NAME --resource-group RG_NAME
az vm stop --name VM_NAME --resource-group RG_NAME
Storage
Bash
Copy code
az storage account list
az storage container list --account-name ACCOUNT_NAME
Networking & Resource Groups
Bash
Copy code
az network vnet list
az network nsg list
az group list
az group create --name MyRG --location eastus
